{"type": "article", "id": 23805, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-14T07:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 2976, "name": "灯饰"}, {"id": 24838, "name": "Lalupo"}, {"id": 24839, "name": "Ningal"}, {"id": 24840, "name": "Maggie Saunders"}, {"id": 24841, "name": "moritz putzier"}, {"id": 24842, "name": "Justin Nagelberg"}, {"id": 24843, "name": "Dominik Pacholczyk"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135005CKFMdArh06qpWzeP.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>FABrics by Ningal </h2>\n<p>这把椅子来自以色列设计师 Ningal，采用桦木结构和经过激光切割皮革，通过 3D 打印的 ABS(工程塑料合金)接口连接，让皮革和桦木“钉”在了一起，有种手工的气质。设计师希望使用这种普通的材料使它能大范围生产，而皮革极有辨识度的颜色增加了这把椅子的时尚气息，让它很适合年轻人。<a href=\"http://www.ningaldesign.com/#!fabrics/ywcc3\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121035QM492jZkYGFhm3vX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121035vrwNXo2VGPxksSu4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021210361yHDqT8d4CnjPUZr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121036P0lqKsgQcrSkuIVT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121037FZ78XkvacfSBVeT5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>NAPKIN HOLDERS by Maggie Saunders</h2>\n<p>这个像积木一样的木制三角块是一个放餐巾的桌面工具，卷好的餐巾可以插入圆孔里，有固定形状的作用，也保持了整齐有序。每一个三角块都含有磁铁，颜色也不同，可以使六个小块拼成一个六角形，完全可以看成一组可玩耍的积木，增加了人和物之间的互动。设计师是萨凡纳艺术设计学院的学生，产品目前还没有生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121037t8lT1wpSCIiXGoM9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121037S3baKtyg5P6dFGY4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021210382QuEjNAXlZzVqWCK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121038Mjo7IQZ92mFRvYA4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121039dECoLjVB1Mfpbi6g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>WBS 70 by Lalupo</h2>\n<p>这个水泥做的方形花瓶灵感源于 1970 年代“东德”的建筑。它的表面被划分成排列整齐的小格子，上面刻有浮雕似的纹理，用深浅颜色来表现门和窗，将原本很单调的建筑形式运用其中，表现出雕塑的极简美，也有一点怀旧。它也可以用做放汤匙等的容器。每一个花瓶都是手工做的，经过了防水处理，售价 100 美元，<a href=\"https://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/wbs-70/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121039z3Y0VTPgpqL964jc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121040HsqxP6m9vXOSgrQE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121040cIBWMroJiLyKvhGs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121041IdEPNOtg1s74blKm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>“inti”灯  by moritz putzier</h2>\n<p>这是一盏可旋转的灯，球形灯体在漏斗形的灯座上。它由两个玻璃球体组成，一个是完全透明的，另一个带有一半的颜色。当旋转球形灯体时，不透明的一半形成了灯罩，遮住了一部分光源，使其方向和角度都不相同，有间接调整光线大小的作用。另外，球形灯体，漏斗形灯座和圆柱形灯座这些不同的几何图形搭配在一起，很可爱，<a href=\"http://www.moritzputzier.com/inti\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121041l8zAFkYEhicuyOPT.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121042bdwOaY01HhSTL5IJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70293399\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121042eVQRIDNx2lkdY7T3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70293399\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121043IC0ZOprGzjB4hb7d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49877751\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121043doZG9yBu14zA7Pj2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49877751\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Sa Umbrella by Justin Nagelberg</h2>\n<p>这把雨伞并没有金属骨架和金属头，它是用可回收塑料制成。手柄底部有用于旋转的弹簧装置，自动沿着伞内的塑料导向板开合，有折纸的感觉，也是极简的设计。此外，塑料材料比起传统的布料有更强的防水性。产品获得了 2015 年的红点奖，目前已完成众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/860103721/satm-the-umbrella-reimagined/description\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121044xfpd46MAzoNUZBrR.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121045z0x3w1kPMhAa52HQ.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121046q0jw7cNOlMmpzK81.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121046M4jAm6KyHfw93hEz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121046CXalnYSq4F3iPULj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61413844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>NAHUA COSMETICS by Dominik Pacholczyk</h2>\n<p>这是瑞士化妆品牌 Nahua Cosmetics 的包装系列，从纸袋、盒子到装化妆品的容器本身一律采用白色，显得很纯净，传达出少用添加剂的意思。花纹和 logo 都用很细的银色线条，通过反光来表现深浅，整体显示出干净和优雅。花纹的灵感源于阿兹特克人（Aztec）的装饰，他们是在墨西哥的印第安人，生产的 chia oil（奇雅子油）被称为快乐精油，可以加工成美容产品或营养保健品。设计师来自波兰，<a href=\"http://www.dominikpacholczyk.com/work/nahua-cosmetics/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121047BCuHvMAPQFRN49ir.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121047ypDkthYz7xjicv4X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121048ZPa7HW0RKiQdgufB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121049szPULOMWYGcpe8FK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121049QjTOfctvz9lsrF4E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}